'''Tal-Yannar Najjan ''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Medic/Legends|medic]] assigned to [[Delta Base]].<ref name="SWAJ10:WBC">{{JournalCite|10|Wanted by Cracken (Star Wars Adventure Journal)}}</ref>

Najjan treated the injuries of New Republic operatives [[Kichiir]] the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]], [[Oollj]], and [[Cith Sninif]] following their attempt to stop the theft of [[Meleenium/Legends|Meleenium]] from the [[Qua'Tahc]] mines on [[Af'El/Legends|Af'El]].<ref name="SWAJ10:WBC" />

